1
00:00:00,000 --> 00:00:10,000
[English subtitles are available]

2
00:00:57,280 --> 00:01:04,670
[We Are Young]

3
00:01:04,760 --> 00:01:07,640
[Episode 17]

4
00:01:23,110 --> 00:01:24,210
I told you

5
00:01:24,300 --> 00:01:26,360
this place is simply uninhabitable.

6
00:01:26,410 --> 00:01:27,860
But you just had to come.

7
00:01:30,020 --> 00:01:31,680
Yon don't have to put on an act.

8
00:01:36,310 --> 00:01:37,190
It's okay.

9
00:01:38,509 --> 00:01:39,700
I'm just homesick.

10
00:01:43,259 --> 00:01:45,150
I had this dream when I was abroad.

11
00:01:45,860 --> 00:01:47,060
Returning to Xiamen.

12
00:01:47,530 --> 00:01:49,110
Lying on a big bed.

13
00:01:50,210 --> 00:01:52,009
You and your mum were there, too.

14
00:01:54,789 --> 00:01:57,300
Should I thank you for remembering us?

15
00:01:58,220 --> 00:01:59,410
But I'm sorry.

16
00:02:00,900 --> 00:02:02,500
You've long been forgotten.

17
00:02:05,650 --> 00:02:06,800
And your plans.

18
00:02:07,370 --> 00:02:08,630
Just stop them at once.

19
00:02:09,610 --> 00:02:11,540
I won't leave the country with you.

20
00:02:20,790 --> 00:02:21,670
Xi Xi.

21
00:02:27,430 --> 00:02:28,690
Take care of yourself.

22
00:02:43,140 --> 00:02:44,270
Where are you going?

23
00:03:11,780 --> 00:03:12,660
Xi Xi.

24
00:03:14,030 --> 00:03:15,230
Uncle Qian just feels

25
00:03:15,300 --> 00:03:17,630
that he owed you too much
when he was young.

26
00:03:18,520 --> 00:03:20,060
He wants to make it up to you.

27
00:03:20,140 --> 00:03:21,680
but has no idea how to do it.

28
00:03:21,990 --> 00:03:22,870
You know that?

29
00:03:23,490 --> 00:03:24,850
Don't worry about it.

30
00:03:34,090 --> 00:03:35,940
If you feel like crying,

31
00:03:36,120 --> 00:03:37,079
I'll just pull over

32
00:03:37,079 --> 00:03:38,740
and let you cry your heart out.

33
00:03:41,880 --> 00:03:42,760
I don't need it.

34
00:03:57,590 --> 00:03:59,610
Now I feel really bad.

35
00:04:08,630 --> 00:04:09,510
You know,

36
00:04:11,010 --> 00:04:13,210
when I was a kid, on every birthday,

37
00:04:14,440 --> 00:04:15,970
I'd wish for him to come home

38
00:04:17,300 --> 00:04:18,760
to keep me and Mum company.

39
00:04:21,040 --> 00:04:22,800
I was always wondering

40
00:04:23,810 --> 00:04:24,910
why Dad couldn't

41
00:04:25,040 --> 00:04:26,710
pick me up from school?

42
00:04:29,790 --> 00:04:31,330
Why couldn't I

43
00:04:31,420 --> 00:04:33,280
receive a birthday gift from Dad?

44
00:04:38,860 --> 00:04:40,530
Whenever I go shopping and see

45
00:04:40,620 --> 00:04:41,590
men's clothing,

46
00:04:43,300 --> 00:04:45,030
it makes me wonder where Dad is.

47
00:04:46,780 --> 00:04:48,409
Will he miss me?

48
00:04:53,290 --> 00:04:55,750
I'll wonder if it was
because I wasn't good enough

49
00:04:55,750 --> 00:04:57,030
that he didn't love me.

50
00:04:58,040 --> 00:04:59,170
He didn't come back.

51
00:04:59,450 --> 00:05:01,110
He's been always away from us.

52
00:05:04,510 --> 00:05:05,970
[You don't have a father.]

53
00:05:06,050 --> 00:05:07,680
[My dad didn't leave me.]

54
00:05:08,820 --> 00:05:10,750
[It's you who don't have a father.]

55
00:05:10,800 --> 00:05:11,770
[It's you.]

56
00:05:12,650 --> 00:05:14,110
[You don't have a father.]

57
00:05:14,360 --> 00:05:16,700
[Ma Li's General Store]

58
00:05:14,360 --> 00:05:15,380
[What's going on?]

59
00:05:18,630 --> 00:05:19,950
[Who are you kids?]

60
00:05:20,040 --> 00:05:22,060
[How dare you bully us?]

61
00:05:22,370 --> 00:05:24,530
[Crazy kids!]

62
00:05:25,760 --> 00:05:28,620
[Mum, where's Dad?]

63
00:05:48,950 --> 00:05:50,000
[Are you hurt?]

64
00:06:02,320 --> 00:06:03,380
[Listen to me.]

65
00:06:05,450 --> 00:06:06,580
[You have a father.]

66
00:06:08,920 --> 00:06:11,080
[He's a famous musician.]

67
00:06:13,410 --> 00:06:15,300
[He's now overseas.]

68
00:06:18,730 --> 00:06:20,010
[You must remember.]

69
00:06:21,420 --> 00:06:23,880
[You're better than all the kids here.]

70
00:06:24,630 --> 00:06:25,820
[Got it?]

71
00:06:29,730 --> 00:06:31,730
[I'm asking you a question. Got it?]

72
00:06:33,340 --> 00:06:34,270
[Yes.]

73
00:06:47,909 --> 00:06:49,400
When I saw him just now,

74
00:06:50,940 --> 00:06:53,010
I didn't feel anything.

75
00:06:55,170 --> 00:06:56,130
Except for rage.

76
00:06:58,600 --> 00:06:59,860
Who does he think he is?

77
00:07:01,020 --> 00:07:02,560
Who is he to barge in

78
00:07:02,650 --> 00:07:04,380
and out of my life as he pleases?

79
00:07:05,240 --> 00:07:06,560
Who is he to ask for love?

80
00:07:06,560 --> 00:07:07,530
From me, even?

81
00:07:08,760 --> 00:07:10,350
He was never there for us.

82
00:07:10,610 --> 00:07:12,330
Now he expects us to love him?

83
00:07:22,140 --> 00:07:24,200
I'm totally clueless.

84
00:07:39,030 --> 00:07:40,530
The truth is,

85
00:07:42,820 --> 00:07:44,180
all I ever wanted

86
00:07:46,640 --> 00:07:49,860
was a normal, peaceful life.

87
00:07:53,550 --> 00:07:54,650
You've seen it.

88
00:07:58,170 --> 00:08:00,110
The things that I want to keep

89
00:08:02,040 --> 00:08:03,360
are all gone.

90
00:08:04,990 --> 00:08:06,990
And the things that I want to discard

91
00:08:10,180 --> 00:08:11,280
keep coming back.

92
00:08:12,650 --> 00:08:14,940
Every failure is a reminder.

93
00:08:15,950 --> 00:08:17,210
A reminder to Qian Xi Xi

94
00:08:18,100 --> 00:08:20,350
that she's an insignificant
blade of grass,

95
00:08:20,350 --> 00:08:23,070
and that she can never change it, ever.

96
00:08:32,179 --> 00:08:33,059
Xi Xi.

97
00:08:33,679 --> 00:08:36,280
You may be a blade of grass
in the eyes of others.

98
00:08:37,370 --> 00:08:39,169
But you're different in my eyes.

99
00:08:39,350 --> 00:08:40,539
In my world,

100
00:08:40,890 --> 00:08:43,419
including the world of
all those who love you,

101
00:08:43,840 --> 00:08:45,700
you're the most important being.

102
00:08:48,110 --> 00:08:49,030
No.

103
00:08:50,310 --> 00:08:52,550
If you feel like crying,

104
00:08:52,640 --> 00:08:54,140
just do it here.

105
00:08:55,150 --> 00:08:56,610
You can cry your heart out.

106
00:08:56,650 --> 00:08:58,010
Let me give you a hug.

107
00:08:59,950 --> 00:09:02,010
Just cry.

108
00:09:02,100 --> 00:09:03,600
Just cry out your sadness.

109
00:09:03,690 --> 00:09:05,090
Then you'll feel better.

110
00:09:07,820 --> 00:09:08,830
Just cry.

111
00:09:25,110 --> 00:09:25,990
It's okay.

112
00:09:27,090 --> 00:09:28,280
Don't stop crying.

113
00:09:29,070 --> 00:09:29,950
Don't stop.

114
00:09:32,060 --> 00:09:33,740
I'm not crying for him.

115
00:09:33,870 --> 00:09:35,760
I know.

116
00:09:43,420 --> 00:09:44,600
Silly girl.

117
00:09:45,620 --> 00:09:47,950
Just cry and you'll feel better.

118
00:10:08,760 --> 00:10:12,810
[Shapowei Art Zone, Art, Life, Live]

119
00:10:16,200 --> 00:10:17,080
Hello.

120
00:10:23,810 --> 00:10:25,270
I have a piece of good news.

121
00:10:25,570 --> 00:10:26,710
You scared me.

122
00:10:26,840 --> 00:10:28,160
Zhang Jia Yun's fan base

123
00:10:28,160 --> 00:10:30,230
has tripled in size.

124
00:10:30,450 --> 00:10:32,850
It isn't showing any signs
of stopping yet.

125
00:10:33,000 --> 00:10:34,150
Of course.

126
00:10:34,630 --> 00:10:35,990
Jiang Zhe Yang is amazing.

127
00:10:35,990 --> 00:10:37,930
He's simply awesome.

128
00:10:38,370 --> 00:10:40,530
I just discovered a pattern.

129
00:10:41,050 --> 00:10:43,470
Jia Yun used to have lots of male fans.

130
00:10:44,130 --> 00:10:46,260
Male fans don't translate into sales.

131
00:10:46,380 --> 00:10:48,840
Since that interactive live stream,

132
00:10:49,850 --> 00:10:51,090
Yang Yang's female fans

133
00:10:51,090 --> 00:10:52,890
have all turned to Zhang Jia Yun.

134
00:10:53,020 --> 00:10:54,710
They support and care for her.

135
00:10:55,220 --> 00:10:57,150
This is why her fan base is growing.

136
00:10:57,510 --> 00:10:58,430
Good for her.

137
00:10:58,650 --> 00:10:59,800
Go tell Xi Xi.

138
00:10:59,890 --> 00:11:01,690
Let Jia Yun do more products.

139
00:11:01,910 --> 00:11:03,440
We should ride on this wave.

140
00:11:05,340 --> 00:11:06,470
What's the time now?

141
00:11:06,790 --> 00:11:08,770
It's been a waste of time.

142
00:11:11,020 --> 00:11:12,480
There's nothing we can do.

143
00:11:16,250 --> 00:11:18,100
Have you arranged tomorrow's job?

144
00:11:18,100 --> 00:11:19,030
No.

145
00:11:19,110 --> 00:11:19,990
Not yet?

146
00:11:21,310 --> 00:11:23,380
What's going on?

147
00:11:23,730 --> 00:11:25,390
I should ask you that instead.

148
00:11:25,540 --> 00:11:27,560
We've been here since early morning.

149
00:11:27,560 --> 00:11:29,020
When we got into the house,

150
00:11:29,060 --> 00:11:30,460
we were abruptly chased out

151
00:11:30,460 --> 00:11:32,220
by the guy living in your house.

152
00:11:33,900 --> 00:11:35,960
He wouldn't have chased
you out for no reason.

153
00:11:35,960 --> 00:11:36,890
We did nothing.

154
00:11:36,980 --> 00:11:38,440
We were as clueless as you.

155
00:11:42,560 --> 00:11:43,440
Tell you what.

156
00:11:45,470 --> 00:11:47,070
One, two, three. four, five.

157
00:11:47,760 --> 00:11:49,650
Here's RMB600. Take it.

158
00:11:50,320 --> 00:11:52,240
It's your payment for the day.

159
00:11:52,330 --> 00:11:54,180
I'll get in touch with you again.

160
00:11:54,490 --> 00:11:55,370
Fine.

161
00:11:56,690 --> 00:11:57,620
I'm sorry, guys.

162
00:11:58,930 --> 00:12:00,430
What a day.

163
00:12:16,180 --> 00:12:17,060
Xi Xi.

164
00:12:17,370 --> 00:12:18,690
What are you doing?

165
00:12:22,520 --> 00:12:24,670
I wanted to renovate this old house.

166
00:12:24,760 --> 00:12:26,170
So I bought some materials.

167
00:12:26,170 --> 00:12:27,970
Those were the renovation workers I hired.

168
00:12:27,970 --> 00:12:29,510
Why did you chase them out?

169
00:12:31,230 --> 00:12:34,030
This faucet was installed incorrectly.

170
00:12:34,130 --> 00:12:36,150
They mixed up the hot and cold water tap.

171
00:12:36,150 --> 00:12:37,350
I had to fix it myself.

172
00:12:39,280 --> 00:12:40,820
What's with you?

173
00:12:41,170 --> 00:12:43,300
Now I've paid the workers for nothing.

174
00:12:43,810 --> 00:12:45,570
I was trying to help.

175
00:12:49,050 --> 00:12:50,980
They came to install the lighting.

176
00:12:51,030 --> 00:12:51,990
Tell me,

177
00:12:52,260 --> 00:12:53,530
who's going to do it?

178
00:12:54,190 --> 00:12:55,730
I'll do it.

179
00:12:55,820 --> 00:12:56,790
Come with me.

180
00:12:56,880 --> 00:12:58,110
Are you sure?

181
00:12:58,640 --> 00:12:59,740
Stop pretending.

182
00:13:00,000 --> 00:13:02,070
You have no idea at all.

183
00:13:02,330 --> 00:13:03,700
Leave the lamps alone.

184
00:13:03,790 --> 00:13:05,390
Wouldn't want to break them.

185
00:13:07,660 --> 00:13:08,540
Fine.

186
00:13:08,630 --> 00:13:11,360
If you think the workers
I hired were unreliable,

187
00:13:11,620 --> 00:13:13,330
why don't you find some that are?

188
00:13:13,330 --> 00:13:14,210
I'll help you.

189
00:13:19,450 --> 00:13:21,450
There're plenty of options online.

190
00:13:22,400 --> 00:13:23,400
Make your choice.

191
00:13:26,450 --> 00:13:28,690
The workers are actually fine.

192
00:13:31,940 --> 00:13:34,190
Don't touch the things in the house.

193
00:13:34,850 --> 00:13:38,020
Don't make decisions on my behalf.

194
00:13:39,950 --> 00:13:40,830
Sure.

195
00:13:41,450 --> 00:13:44,350
I'll find someone to install the lighting.

196
00:13:44,570 --> 00:13:47,030
Just leave the things
alone. I'll handle it.

197
00:13:53,590 --> 00:13:56,410
Why on earth are you
installing the wallpaper?

198
00:13:57,600 --> 00:13:59,090
All the other walls are done.

199
00:13:59,090 --> 00:14:00,410
Except this one.

200
00:14:00,630 --> 00:14:01,910
I thought it was left out.

201
00:14:01,910 --> 00:14:03,360
So I installed it.

202
00:14:03,710 --> 00:14:05,470
You've created a mess.

203
00:14:06,040 --> 00:14:08,110
Stop doing it.

204
00:14:08,240 --> 00:14:09,520
You're damaging the wall.

205
00:14:09,520 --> 00:14:11,410
Didn't you see there's something inside?

206
00:14:11,410 --> 00:14:12,940
Is it something important?

207
00:14:13,390 --> 00:14:15,110
Mum drew this for me.

208
00:14:20,390 --> 00:14:21,990
Do you think it's important?

209
00:14:23,820 --> 00:14:25,400
I don't know.

210
00:14:54,270 --> 00:14:55,470
What's with your dad?

211
00:14:57,920 --> 00:14:59,320
He was giving me trouble.

212
00:15:01,260 --> 00:15:02,580
Are you all right?

213
00:15:03,420 --> 00:15:04,300
I'm just fine.

214
00:15:05,490 --> 00:15:06,890
All is well over here.

215
00:15:07,200 --> 00:15:08,740
We have two new potential clients.

216
00:15:08,740 --> 00:15:10,140
They wish to work with us.

217
00:15:10,190 --> 00:15:12,170
Just be open with your dad.

218
00:15:12,260 --> 00:15:13,580
Talk it over with him.

219
00:15:14,330 --> 00:15:15,930
The company is in good hands.

220
00:15:16,270 --> 00:15:17,940
Thanks.

221
00:15:19,350 --> 00:15:20,310
No problem.

222
00:15:20,400 --> 00:15:22,060
Everything here will be fine.

223
00:15:22,210 --> 00:15:24,270
Just talk to your dad.

224
00:15:25,150 --> 00:15:27,490
I'll get back as soon as I can.

225
00:15:29,730 --> 00:15:30,610
Okay.

226
00:15:36,110 --> 00:15:39,360
You can talk to me about
your proposals, gentlemen.

227
00:15:40,420 --> 00:15:42,150
I'm one of the decision makers.

228
00:15:44,820 --> 00:15:45,880
Let me repeat.

229
00:15:46,400 --> 00:15:48,340
If the workers come again,

230
00:15:48,910 --> 00:15:50,320
don't chase them out.

231
00:16:12,540 --> 00:16:18,440
[Shapowei Art Zone]

232
00:16:18,350 --> 00:16:20,550
Those of you who like the skirt

233
00:16:20,680 --> 00:16:22,180
or the blouse,

234
00:16:22,260 --> 00:16:23,520
place your orders now.

235
00:16:23,580 --> 00:16:25,740
That's all for today.

236
00:16:25,830 --> 00:16:28,250
I'll see you all tomorrow.

237
00:16:28,950 --> 00:16:30,010
Bye.

238
00:16:33,130 --> 00:16:34,140
How was it?

239
00:16:37,440 --> 00:16:38,700
Don't be discouraged.

240
00:16:39,030 --> 00:16:41,270
We haven't had live
streams for quite a while.

241
00:16:41,270 --> 00:16:42,720
We'll be fine next time.

242
00:16:44,170 --> 00:16:45,320
What's it?

243
00:16:46,550 --> 00:16:47,780
It's the products.

244
00:16:48,270 --> 00:16:50,770
All the good products
are in Jia Yun's hands.

245
00:16:53,990 --> 00:16:56,390
She did very well in
her recent live stream.

246
00:16:56,890 --> 00:16:59,150
We still have the highest number of fans.

247
00:17:00,190 --> 00:17:01,160
Don't worry.

248
00:17:05,910 --> 00:17:07,760
Xiao Bu, where's Qing Qing?

249
00:17:08,069 --> 00:17:10,349
She used to be my assistant,

250
00:17:10,710 --> 00:17:12,240
I can't seem to find her now.

251
00:17:12,599 --> 00:17:13,520
She...

252
00:17:13,609 --> 00:17:16,069
She's temporarily assigned
to assist Jia Yun.

253
00:17:16,069 --> 00:17:17,670
They're all busy over there.

254
00:17:18,410 --> 00:17:19,589
Okay.

255
00:17:22,010 --> 00:17:22,890
Let's go.

256
00:17:29,190 --> 00:17:30,240
Hello, Ms Qian.

257
00:17:30,460 --> 00:17:31,340
Hello.

258
00:17:31,560 --> 00:17:32,840
We're the renovation company

259
00:17:32,750 --> 00:17:35,410
[Rui Live]

260
00:17:32,930 --> 00:17:34,690
-that you booked on 58.com.
-Ms Qian.

261
00:17:34,690 --> 00:17:35,740
You have a parcel.

262
00:17:36,230 --> 00:17:38,730
The lighting installation
will be at 5 p.m. tomorrow.

263
00:17:38,730 --> 00:17:39,690
Sure.

264
00:17:40,050 --> 00:17:41,810
You have all the necessary accessories

265
00:17:41,810 --> 00:17:44,580
and equipment, right?

266
00:17:45,020 --> 00:17:46,560
We're professional renovators.

267
00:17:46,560 --> 00:17:48,360
Rest assured, we'll get it done.

268
00:17:48,980 --> 00:17:50,910
We'll get in touch again tomorrow.

269
00:17:51,100 --> 00:17:53,380
-Sure, bye.
-Okay, thanks.

270
00:17:55,230 --> 00:17:56,380
Sign here.

271
00:18:02,100 --> 00:18:03,020
I won't

272
00:18:04,600 --> 00:18:06,850
argue with you about the products.

273
00:18:07,770 --> 00:18:09,880
Now we don't even get an assistant.

274
00:18:11,160 --> 00:18:12,420
This is unacceptable.

275
00:18:13,010 --> 00:18:14,540
What's the meaning of this?

276
00:18:21,060 --> 00:18:23,080
And I saw that person.

277
00:18:23,260 --> 00:18:25,500
What's her name? Cola? Sprite?

278
00:18:25,810 --> 00:18:28,340
She had the nerve to steal
our dressing table.

279
00:18:30,480 --> 00:18:32,810
How dare those small fries

280
00:18:32,900 --> 00:18:34,430
encroach on our territory?

281
00:18:35,620 --> 00:18:38,000
Alright. Stop complaining.

282
00:18:39,230 --> 00:18:40,200
You know,

283
00:18:40,460 --> 00:18:41,960
the way you're acting now

284
00:18:42,050 --> 00:18:43,280
reminds me

285
00:18:43,370 --> 00:18:45,790
of a kid crying for candy.

286
