00:37:45,830 --> 00:37:47,950
It's lunch time now,
yet you expect me to work.

565
00:37:47,950 --> 00:37:50,100
Can't you just give me a break?

566
00:37:52,300 --> 00:37:53,530
That's not what I meant.

567
00:37:53,530 --> 00:37:55,160
If you want to watch a show,

568
00:37:55,250 --> 00:37:56,980
there's nothing wrong with it.

569
00:38:01,630 --> 00:38:02,990
Fine, Mr Duan.

570
00:38:03,300 --> 00:38:05,330
I just hate it when my boss takes
an interest in me.

571
00:38:05,330 --> 00:38:07,330
Tell me, are you here for something?

572
00:38:10,560 --> 00:38:11,440
Yes.

573
00:38:14,520 --> 00:38:16,720
Well, Jia Yun,

574
00:38:18,000 --> 00:38:19,580
look at our company

575
00:38:20,460 --> 00:38:22,310
and how big it's grown.

576
00:38:23,810 --> 00:38:25,700
What is it still missing?

577
00:38:26,180 --> 00:38:28,030
If I'm not mistaken,

578
00:38:28,120 --> 00:38:30,050
you're talking about

579
00:38:30,670 --> 00:38:32,600
the position of head broadcaster.

580
00:38:34,190 --> 00:38:36,740
I like smart people like you.

581
00:38:37,270 --> 00:38:39,420
Now our company

582
00:38:39,510 --> 00:38:41,140
needs a head broadcaster.

583
00:38:41,800 --> 00:38:43,520
We have several candidates.

584
00:38:43,820 --> 00:38:44,700
Yuan Yuan

585
00:38:45,580 --> 00:38:47,780
just came back to us, right?

586
00:38:48,440 --> 00:38:49,540
Xi Xi

587
00:38:50,160 --> 00:38:52,820
is busy mending a
relationship with her father.

588
00:38:53,280 --> 00:38:55,660
The rest of them

589
00:38:55,750 --> 00:38:57,900
such as Yuan Bao and Little Duckling

590
00:38:58,780 --> 00:39:00,320
are not up to mark yet.

591
00:39:01,250 --> 00:39:03,840
I stay up every night, thinking,

592
00:39:04,240 --> 00:39:07,140
"Who should be our head broadcaster?"

593
00:39:11,190 --> 00:39:12,690
Who?

594
00:39:14,540 --> 00:39:16,690
Then it hit me. Jia Yun.

595
00:39:16,960 --> 00:39:18,500
You're the girl, Jia Yun.

596
00:39:19,600 --> 00:39:22,660
You're merely choosing the
best of a bad bunch, Mr Duan.

597
00:39:22,680 --> 00:39:23,950
Not at all.

598
00:39:24,040 --> 00:39:25,580
That's not what I meant.

599
00:39:26,200 --> 00:39:28,090
Sure, I'm not among the bad bunch.

600
00:39:28,530 --> 00:39:30,950
But you know me well.

601
00:39:31,040 --> 00:39:33,670
I'm used to a more relaxed pace.

602
00:39:34,470 --> 00:39:37,020
When it comes to competitions and whatnot,

603
00:39:37,110 --> 00:39:38,840
I have absolutely no interest.

604
00:39:38,870 --> 00:39:41,950
I know you well.

605
00:39:42,960 --> 00:39:46,570
We have grown considerably,

606
00:39:47,010 --> 00:39:48,020
haven't we?

607
00:39:48,110 --> 00:39:49,910
Now the company needs you.

608
00:39:50,880 --> 00:39:52,290
It's time you step up.

609
00:39:53,170 --> 00:39:55,810
Otherwise, look around you.

610
00:39:55,890 --> 00:39:58,580
There's nobody else, right?

611
00:40:00,210 --> 00:40:01,610
So you haven't heard.

612
00:40:04,390 --> 00:40:07,510
This morning, a miracle happened

613
00:40:07,600 --> 00:40:09,400
to one of our employees.

614
00:40:11,250 --> 00:40:12,390
Who's that?

615
00:40:17,320 --> 00:40:18,600
Take a look at this.

616
00:40:29,030 --> 00:40:30,790
What's Yuan Yuan doing?

617
00:40:33,340 --> 00:40:34,530
What's this?

618
00:40:34,310 --> 00:40:36,860
[Cat on the Roof]

619
00:40:35,050 --> 00:40:36,280
A piano trio?

620
00:40:52,390 --> 00:40:53,360
Hello, Uncle Qian.

621
00:40:53,360 --> 00:40:54,240
You look busy.

622
00:40:54,460 --> 00:40:55,920
I've been waiting for you.

623
00:40:56,220 --> 00:40:57,270
Lunch for Xi Xi.

624
00:40:57,400 --> 00:40:59,030
I got the address from your dad.

625
00:40:59,030 --> 00:41:00,350
I know. My dad asked me

626
00:41:00,440 --> 00:41:01,540
to wait for you here.

627
00:41:01,540 --> 00:41:02,600
What are you watching?

628
00:41:02,600 --> 00:41:04,050
It's a piano video.

629
00:41:07,740 --> 00:41:09,860
Isn't that me?

630
00:41:12,580 --> 00:41:14,740
No wonder that person looks like you.

631
00:41:14,830 --> 00:41:15,800
It really is you.

632
00:41:15,880 --> 00:41:17,280
I was passing by that day.

633
00:41:18,260 --> 00:41:20,240
I heard you used to be a pianist.

634
00:41:20,330 --> 00:41:22,620
It's all in the past.

635
00:41:23,230 --> 00:41:24,690
I need to give this to Xi Xi.

636
00:41:24,770 --> 00:41:26,750
She's inside. Come with me.

637
00:41:27,540 --> 00:41:28,640
Xi Xi.

638
00:41:28,730 --> 00:41:31,240
Not only have I slept in a container,

639
00:41:31,330 --> 00:41:32,430
worked in a factory,

640
00:41:32,430 --> 00:41:34,430
I have also worked in many kitchens.

641
00:41:35,290 --> 00:41:37,710
So I made some dishes for you.

642
00:41:38,060 --> 00:41:39,730
You're really talented, Uncle Qian.

643
00:41:39,730 --> 00:41:41,840
Let's eat together.

644
00:41:41,930 --> 00:41:42,940
Dig in, guys.

645
00:41:43,030 --> 00:41:44,570
-Thanks, Uncle Qian.
-Jia Yun, Duan Ran.

646
00:41:44,570 --> 00:41:46,300
Everyone is welcome to join us.

647
00:41:46,510 --> 00:41:49,230
This is the benefit of
having him as a father.

648
00:41:49,450 --> 00:41:50,770
Give me a break.

649
00:41:50,860 --> 00:41:53,330
-Isn't it overcooked?
-No.

650
00:41:53,790 --> 00:41:55,020
Are these buns?

651
00:41:55,130 --> 00:41:56,230
They're shumai.

652
00:41:56,320 --> 00:41:57,810
-Try it.
-Look, wotou.

653
00:41:57,900 --> 00:41:59,050
Let's try the dim sum.

654
00:41:59,050 --> 00:42:00,450
Let me help you.

655
00:42:01,290 --> 00:42:02,420
I just want to say...

656
00:42:03,450 --> 00:42:04,330
Uncle Qian.

657
00:42:08,330 --> 00:42:10,400
It's so delicious.

658
00:42:11,010 --> 00:42:12,730
You ate a lot.

659
00:42:12,820 --> 00:42:14,140
It's really good.

660
00:42:14,970 --> 00:42:16,570
There are still plenty more.

661
00:42:18,100 --> 00:42:19,200
Mr Duan.

662
00:42:19,330 --> 00:42:21,460
The broadcasters
are waiting for you.

663
00:42:23,470 --> 00:42:25,270
-The workforce mobilisation meeting.
-Okay.

664
00:42:25,270 --> 00:42:26,330
Just a moment.

665
00:42:26,500 --> 00:42:27,700
What meeting is that?

666
00:42:27,780 --> 00:42:28,890
Mobilise what?

667
00:42:29,140 --> 00:42:30,370
Don't you know?

668
00:42:30,810 --> 00:42:33,410
Mr Duan wants our broadcasters
to vie for the Talent Chart.

669
00:42:33,410 --> 00:42:35,470
We're having a meeting to discuss it.

670
00:42:37,500 --> 00:42:38,600
Duan Ran.

671
00:42:39,040 --> 00:42:40,450
Are you kidding me?

672
00:42:40,800 --> 00:42:41,810
The Talent Chart?

673
00:42:41,900 --> 00:42:43,570
Only head broadcasters stand a chance.

674
00:42:43,570 --> 00:42:44,570
We don't have one.

675
00:42:46,700 --> 00:42:48,500
We'll discuss it in the meeting.

676
00:42:50,520 --> 00:42:51,670
Can't you wait?

677
00:42:53,160 --> 00:42:54,880
We'll be there in a moment.

678
00:42:56,330 --> 00:42:58,660
I have a meeting now. Enjoy your meal.

679
00:42:58,750 --> 00:42:59,750
Finish your meal.

680
00:42:59,760 --> 00:43:01,740
You've eaten enough, let's go.

681
00:43:01,830 --> 00:43:02,930
-I'm eating.
-Let's go.

682
00:43:02,930 --> 00:43:04,870
-Can't we finish our meal first?
-Come on.
